http://localhost:8080


Create Profile (POST)
✔️ Endpoint: http://localhost:8080/api/profile
Tests: Ensure a profile can be created, photo can be uploaded, and a valid response is returned.
Get All Profiles (GET)

✔️ Endpoint: http://localhost:8080/api/profile
Tests: Ensure all profiles are listed in the response.
Get Profile by ID (GET)

✔️ Endpoint: http://localhost:8080/api/profile/{id}
Tests: Ensure the correct profile is returned when providing a valid ID.
Update Profile (PUT)

✔️ Endpoint: http://localhost:8080/api/profile/{id}
Tests: Ensure profile can be updated, and check that the photo URL remains valid after updates.
Delete Profile (DELETE)

✔️ Endpoint: http://localhost:8080/api/profile/{id}
Tests: Ensure the profile is deleted correctly, and the response status is appropriate.